text: Daniel Finěk (born 25 May 2000) is a Czech professional football defender currently playing for FK Varnsdorf on loan from FC Hradec Králové in the Czech National Football League. == Club career == He made his league debut in Hradec's Czech National Football League 1–0 win at Táborsko on 22 July 2018. == References == == External links == * Daniel Finěk official international statistics * * Daniel Finěk profile on the FC Hradec Králové official website Category:Czech footballers Category:Czech Republic youth international footballers Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Czech National Football League players Category:FC Hradec Králové players Category:FK Varnsdorf players Category:Association football defenders
